 <i>before a live studio audience.</i> 

00:04.604 --> 00:07.506
Hey, Miss Howe, I was over      
at the magic shop today,        

00:07.574 --> 00:09.608
and look what I got             
for Halloween. Aah!             

00:13.113 --> 00:14.680
