bloody thumb!                   

00:14.781 --> 00:15.948
                    Yuck!       

00:16.082 --> 00:17.316
  You just hide it somewhere,   

00:17.384 --> 00:19.284
and then get ready for the fun. 

00:20.720 --> 00:23.856
This was a Halloween night      
tradition around our house.     

00:23.957 --> 00:26.859
