              scary, just gross.

00:33.233 --> 00:35.534
         That's 'cause          
 you haven't seen it in action. 

00:36.970 --> 00:38.971
I'll try it out                 
on Mr. Peterson.                

00:39.105 --> 00:41.073
                     Wood, can I
                  have a refill?

00:41.174 --> 00:42.541
Sure thing,                     
Mr. P.                          

00:42.609 --> 00:44.410
        Way ahead               
            of you.             
                      All right.

00:44.511 --> 00:46.412
             Yuck.              

00:50.717 --> 00:52.584
     What the hell is that?     

00:52.652 --> 00:55.320
     The old bloody thumb.      

00:55.388 --> 00:56.922
Didn't it scare you?            

00:56.990 --> 01:00.392
No, actually, Wood, it's really 
 more gross than anything else. 

01:00.460 --> 01:01.694
                    Told you.   

01:01.761 --> 01:02.895
Here's another beer, Norm.      

01:02.962 --> 01:05.164
