                  Gary...       

06:57.150 --> 06:58.417
CARLA:                          
Yeah.                           

06:58.551 --> 07:01.353
Oh... Oh, that's it, man.       

07:01.421 --> 07:02.988
    I'm calling Gary,           

07:03.056 --> 07:05.624
      and I'm telling him       
  that payback is on its way.   

07:05.692 --> 07:07.259
         (over phone):          
     ¶ ...Do the vampire ¶      

