(music playing over phone)      

07:10.063 --> 07:12.498
            ¶ Hey! ¶            

07:12.565 --> 07:14.199
      ¶ Do the twist... ¶       

07:15.335 --> 07:17.269
          ¶ Yeah... ¶           

07:19.439 --> 07:20.673
    ¶ Do it with... ¶           

07:24.744 --> 07:26.245
        He's good.              

07:27.781 --> 07:29.148
     You know, this is just     
      the beginning, too.       

07:29.215 --> 07:30.616
    He's gonna be doing this    
         all day long.          

07:30.684 --> 07:32.151
        We're gonna have        
     to think of something      

07:32.218 --> 07:33.452
to really get back at him.      

07:33.520 --> 07:34.620
                 Yeah.          
                          CARLA:
                        Yeah....

